In [4]:
## 建立训练集和测试集
## train_X(训练集数据集X)，train_Y(训练集目标值Y);
## test_X(测试集数据集X)，test_Y(测试集目标值Y);
## 裁剪后的图像尺寸为IMG_HEIGHT，IMG_WIDTH
train_X=[];train_Y=[]
test_X=[];test_Y=[]
IMG_HEIGHT=IMG_WIDTH=100
sys.stdout.flush()
train_folders=next(os.walk(train_dir))[1]
test_folders=next(os.walk(test_dir))[1]
print('开始读训练集图像文件...')
for folder in train_folders:
    PATH=os.path.join(train_dir,folder)
    train_imgs=os.listdir(PATH)
    print('读文件夹'+folder)
    for n, id_ in tqdm(enumerate(train_imgs), total=len(train_imgs)):
        train_img_path=os.path.join(PATH,id_)
        I=img.imread(train_img_path)
        ## rgb图像转灰度图像
        gray=color.rgb2gray(I)
        ## 图像裁剪为100*100统一尺寸
        cropped_img= resize(gray, (IMG_HEIGHT, IMG_WIDTH), mode='constant', preserve_range=True)
        vec_img=cropped_img.reshape(-1)
        train_X.append(vec_img)
        
        train_Y.append(folder)
    print('文件夹'+folder+'读完成!\n')
print('训练集图像文件读完成!!!\n')

print('开始读测试集图像文件...')
for folder in test_folders:
    PATH=os.path.join(test_dir,folder)
    test_imgs=os.listdir(PATH)
    for id_ in test_imgs:
        test_img_path=os.path.join(PATH,id_)
        I=img.imread(test_img_path)
        ## rgb图像转灰度图像
        gray=color.rgb2gray(I)
        ## 图像裁剪为100*100统一尺寸
        cropped_img= resize(gray, (IMG_HEIGHT, IMG_WIDTH), mode='constant', preserve_range=True)
        vec_img=cropped_img.reshape(-1)
        test_X.append(vec_img)
        
        test_Y.append(folder)
print('测试集图像文件读完成!!!')

## 标签train_Y,test_Y转为one_hot coding(独热编码)
map_dic={'buildings':[1,0,0,0,0,0],'forest':[0,1,0,0,0,0],\
        'glacier':[0,0,1,0,0,0],'mountain':[0,0,0,1,0,0],\
        'sea':[0,0,0,0,1,0],'street':[0,0,0,0,0,1]}

In [33]:
def ret_label(one_hot_list):
    '''给定一个独热编码后的列表，返回map_dic的键，如输入[1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]，返回building'''
    for _ in map_dic.items():
        if one_hot_list in _:
            return (_[0])
In [37]:
def show(img,label):
    '''给定numpy数组类型的图像，和标签label，作可视化'''
    fig=plt.figure(figsize=(12,12))
    for i in range(64):
        plt.subplot(8,8,i+1)
        plt.imshow(img[i].reshape(100,100),cmap='gray')
        plt.title("{0}".format(ret_label(label[i].tolist())))
        plt.axis('off')
    plt.show()

搭建线性分类神经网络¶

In [58]:
num_classes=6
W=tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([num_features,num_classes]),name='weight')
b=tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([1,1]),name='weight')

x_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,shape=(None,num_features))
y_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,shape=(None,num_classes))

y_pred=tf.matmul(x_,W)+b
##****************#####
cost=tf.reduce_mean(tf.nn.softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits_v2(logits=y_pred,labels=y_))
train_step=tf.train.AdamOptimizer(0.001).minimize(cost)
#####evaluate model#####
correct_pred=tf.equal(tf.argmax(y_pred,1),tf.argmax(y_,1))
accuracy=tf.reduce_mean(tf.cast(correct_pred,tf.float32))

saver=tf.train.Saver()
with tf.Session() as sess:
    sess.run(tf.global_variables_initializer())
    for i  in range(3800):
        sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x_:train_X_shuffle_pca,y_:train_Y_shuffle})
        if (i+1)%100==0:
            print("训练次数",(i+1))
            train_acc=sess.run(accuracy,feed_dict={x_:train_X_shuffle_pca,y_:train_Y_shuffle})
            print("训练准确率为:",train_acc)
    saver.save(sess,'E:/Python/workspace/Intel_model.ckpt')
    print('模型保存完成！')

In [61]:
##合并训练和测试集数据
D_shuffle=np.concatenate((train_X_shuffle,test_X_shuffle),axis=0)
### 将10000维数据降维到2000
num_features=200
pca = PCA(n_components=num_features)
pca.fit(D_shuffle)
D_shuffle_pca=pca.transform(D_shuffle)
num_train_sample=train_X_shuffle.shape[0]
train_X_pca_shuffle=D_shuffle_pca[:num_train_sample]
test_X_pca_shuffle=D_shuffle_pca[num_train_sample]
train_X_shuffle_pca=D_shuffle_pca[:num_train_sample]
test_X_shuffle_pca=D_shuffle_pca[num_train_sample:]
num_classes=6
W=tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([num_features,num_classes]),name='weight')
b=tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([1,1]),name='weight')

x_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,shape=(None,num_features))
y_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,shape=(None,num_classes))

y_pred=tf.matmul(x_,W)+b
##****************#####
cost=tf.reduce_mean(tf.nn.softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits_v2(logits=y_pred,labels=y_))
train_step=tf.train.AdamOptimizer(0.01).minimize(cost)
#####evaluate model#####
correct_pred=tf.equal(tf.argmax(y_pred,1),tf.argmax(y_,1))
accuracy=tf.reduce_mean(tf.cast(correct_pred,tf.float32))

saver=tf.train.Saver()
with tf.Session() as sess:
    sess.run(tf.global_variables_initializer())
    for i  in range(1000):
        sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x_:train_X_shuffle_pca,y_:train_Y_shuffle})
        if (i+1)%100==0:
            print("训练次数",(i+1))
            train_acc=sess.run(accuracy,feed_dict={x_:train_X_shuffle_pca,y_:train_Y_shuffle})
            print("训练准确率为:",train_acc)
    saver.save(sess,'E:/Python/workspace/Intel_model_200.ckpt')
    print('模型保存完成！')
with tf.Session() as sess:
    ##取回模型
    saver.restore(sess,'E:/Python/workspace/Intel_model_200.ckpt')
    test_acc=sess.run(accuracy,feed_dict={x_:test_X_shuffle_pca,y_:test_Y_shuffle})
    print("测试准确率为:",test_acc)
